  "body": "\r\n***Type***: Bug\r\n\r\n***Summary***: When `Sign message` screen is opened from Dapp - the password pop-up which appears overlaps `Cancel ... Sign` buttons on iPhoneX.\r\n \r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n<img width=\"371\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-09-18 at 14 32 56\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/45684699-c400d700-bb4f-11e8-8aa6-6f36b420fffb.png\">\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n<img width=\"308\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-09-18 at 14 32 40\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/45684705-c95e2180-bb4f-11e8-8503-854cb2242dcf.png\">\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status and log in to account\r\n- Navigate to `Simple Test Dapp` -> `Transactions`\r\n- Tap `Sign message` button\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: Develop\r\n* Operating System:  iOS (iPhoneX)\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\nhttps://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803590-status/builds/8596607/sessions/4401753082/?accessToken=f/U-1B0iauIESYORfY9NTzbfmcs\n\n<blockquote><div><strong><a href=\"https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803590-status/builds/8596607/sessions/4401753082/?accessToken=f/U-1B0iauIESYORfY9NTzbfmcs\">TestFairy: Status 0.9.28 (8472) @2018</a></strong></div></blockquote>",
